---
title: Cheeseburger Inspired Sloppy Joe with Pumpkin Seed and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Cheeseburger Inspired Sloppy Joe in just 15 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R08_W41_UK_UQ16459-3_Main__5low-3ea8873d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/64d24c51317ec2bf51927ebf.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/cheeseburger-inspired-sloppy-joe-64d24c51317ec2bf51927ebf
author: Lily Stevens
servings: 2
time required: 10m
nutrition:
  calories: 700 kcal
  fat: 47.9 g
